      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at our quarterly report and noticed our shrinkage numbers for the electronics warehouse jumped up like 15% this month. i need to figure out how much this is messing with our inventory turnover ratio. can you walk me through how to factor that loss into the calculation?",
